&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong intuition and deep thinking with data sets - Designs new alphas, understands complex systems; knows where to start, or ask others where to start&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrates strong “hacking” ability to quickly get into data to look for empirical relationships and decipher noise or signal&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with classical statistical methods and knows when and how to apply them in a rigorous fashion; Easily learns how to apply new statistical methods; will seek out and learn new methods to better solve problem
